		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Weapon (@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.ntmAbPMerRRj93Jy]{Mace}) - Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><em>Maces, larger than a club, tend to have a cap designed specifically for combat, and are of limited use for anything else.</em></p><p>While you hold this weapon, it sheds Bright Light in a 20-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 20 feet.</p><p><strong>Attack</strong></p><p>When you hit a &amp;reference[Fiend] or an &amp;reference[Undead], it takes an extra [[/damage 2d6 Radiant]] damage.</p><p>If the target has 25 Hit Points or fewer after this damage, it must succeed on a [[/save WIS 15]]{DC 15 Wisdom Save} or be destroyed. On a success, it is &amp;Reference[Frightened] until the end of your next turn.</p><p><strong>Properties:</strong></p><p>&amp;reference[magic weapon]</p>",
